      "title": "Govt and Govt approved private schools to resume activities on 25th July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Government and Government approved private schools will resume academic activities from 25th July.",
        "Accordingly, when schools resume, students will be expected to come to school on Mondays, Tuesdays and Thursdays, while online learning methods will be observed on Wednesdays and Fridays, the Education Ministry said.",
        "According to the press release, the Ministry of Education has advised Provincial Education Secretaries, Provincial Education Directors, Regional Education Directors, Divisional Directors and Assistant Education Directors, in addition to all Principals in this regard.",
        "Govt and Govt approved private schools to resume activities on 25th July"
      ],
